e-free-magcam-security-camera-price-specs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911395/tp-link-tapo-wire-free-magcam-security-camera-price-specs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911395/tp-link-tapo-wire-free-magcam-security-camera-price-specs</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-10T16:12:09-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-10T16:12:09-04:00</updated><title> iRobot 的 Roomba i4 Evo 和 j7 Plus 已降至迄今为止最优惠的价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;iRobot Roomba i4 Evo 靠在墙上的自动清空底座上的居中图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7kN9bCqLDJrcIwA9fKUUpdIti-g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72741781/jtuohy_220325_5101_0015.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;经济实惠的 Roomba i4 Evo 在 Prime Big Deal Days 促销，起价仅为 199.99 美元，比一般售价低 100 美元。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;PFYmXQ&quot;>;与智能锁、可视门铃和其他智能家居技术非常相似，廉价的扫地机器人在过去几年中取得了长足的进步。举个例子？ &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0927GSS6C?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;iRobot 超实惠的 Roomba i4 Evo&lt; /a>;，一款出色的清洁伴侣，作为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23903764/amazon-october-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2023 的一部分，正在大幅降价&quot;>;亚马逊十月 Prime 会员日&lt;/a>;。现在，您可以&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0927GSS6C/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;仅需 199.99 美元&lt; /a>;（折扣 200 美元），比平时的售价 299.99 美元低 100 美元。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;iotDUf&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;最好的预算机器人吸尘器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23846479/best-budget-robot-vacuum-robot-mop&quot;},{ &quot;title&quot;:&quot